'''Iron equipment''' are items made from [[Metal#Basic metals|iron metal]]. Iron equipment is stronger than [[bronze equipment]], but weaker than [[steel equipment]]. All iron items are coloured dark-grey. Iron armour requires 1 [[Defence]] to wield, weapons require 1 [[Attack]], which makes it a suitable alternative to bronze equipment, which has the same requirements.

==Weapons==
'''Iron weapons''' require an [[Attack]] level of 1 to wield.

===One-handed melee weapons===
