===Two-handed melee weapons===
{{Infotable Bonuses|Iron claws|Iron spear#(unp)|Iron 2h sword|Iron halberd|sort=str|nototals=yes}}

===Ranged weapons and ammo===
{{Infotable Bonuses|Iron crossbow|Iron bolts#Unpoisoned|Iron arrow#(unp)|Iron brutal|Iron dart#(unp)|Iron javelin#Unpoisoned|Iron thrownaxe|Iron knife#(unp)|sort=rstr|nototals=yes}}

==Armour==
'''Iron armour''' is the second-lowest quality [[armour]] in the standard spectrum of metal armours ([[Bronze equipment#Armour|bronze]] to [[Dragon equipment#Armour|dragon]]). Iron armour requires 1 [[Defence]] to wear.

{{Infotable Bonuses|Iron med helm|Iron full helm|Iron chainbody|Iron platebody|Iron platelegs|Iron plateskirt|Iron sq shield|Iron kiteshield|Iron boots|Iron gloves|Iron defender#Normal|sort=dslash|nototals=yes}}

==Other==
[[Iron trimmed armour|Trimmed]] and [[Iron gold-trimmed armour|gold-trimmed]] iron armour have the same bonuses as standard iron armour. These can be obtained from the member's only [[Treasure Trails]] minigame.

'''Note:''' Other players '''''cannot''''' trim or bless armour. Players claiming to do so are scammers.

